headline.main: Zambia's Bwalya Pulls Out of FIFA Council Race
headline.print_headline: Zambia's Bwalya Pulls Out of FIFA Council Race

lead_paragraph: A photo of former presidential candidate Hillary Clinton glancing at a newspaper headline about U.S. Vice President Mike Pence using private email has gone viral on social media, with thousands of people commenting on it.
